HAWK-I RRM:

Two parts:

1. Look for new trigger:
	a. GRB???
	b. Mounted; yes/no
	c. if Mounted; Observability; yes/no
	d. if Mounted; if Observable;  Make trigger lock

2. Check triggers:

	OPTIONS:
		1. New trigger GRBNAME.rrm
		2. New trigger, triggered GRBNAME.rrmlock

	a. Trigger lock exists; yes/no
	b. if Trigger exists; New; yes/no
	c. if Trigger exists; if New;
		
		c.1. Upload FTP file
		c.2. E-mail details
		c.3. Finding Chart
		(c.4. text message)

Binaries

	Observability (pyservatory)
		obs/hawki_schedule.py
		
	Mounted		(pyweb)
		hawki_mounted.py

	Trigger details (pyweb)
		hawki_burstinfo.py

	E-mail details
		hawki_email_send.py
		email_filled.txt FILE

	Finding Chart
		hawki_make_fc.py

	Upload FTP file
		hawki_ftp_upload.py
		rrm_template.txt FILE

Libraries
	
	PyServatory

